Azure Cosmos DB is a fully managed, globally distributed, multi-model NoSQL database service designed for low latency, high availability, 
and elastic scalability. It supports various data models (documents, key-value, graph, columnar) and provides turnkey global distribution 
with 99.999% availability SLAs. It is heavily optimized for modern AI applications, offering integrated vector search and No-ETL analytical capabilities.


Important concepts:

- Non relational database
- Document/item in container
- Partition key -- to equally distribute data in the container.
                -- Data distribute in logical partitions
